text: Dirk Kempthorne (born October 29, 1951) was the United States Secretary of the Interior. Kempthorne was the 30th Governor of Idaho. He is a member of the U.S. Republican Party. Kempthorne was born in San Diego, California. Kempthorne graduated from the University of Idaho. He is married to Patricia Kempthorne.
